Class ARParseFormatInfoImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.qual.ARParseFormatInfoImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ARParseFormatInfo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssignParseFormatInfoImpl

    public class ARParseFormatInfoImpl
extends Object
implements ARParseFormatInfo
    Implements the interface ARParseFormatInfo. Holds all the information that would be needed to parse a qualification to build a QualifierInfo object.
